🧠 TaskFlow – Smart To-Do Web App---------------------------------------------------------------------------

TaskFlow is a simple and modern To-Do web application built using HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript. 
It is designed to help users manage daily tasks efficiently with a clean and responsive interface.

The project works completely in the browser using localStorage, so no backend or database is required.

🎯 Purpose of the Project------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The goal of this project is to demonstrate how a real-world productivity application can be
 built using only frontend technologies. It includes user login, task management, and reminders,
  while maintaining a modern and responsive UI.

✨ Features----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔐 Login and Signup--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-Users can create an account using a username and password
-Login system is handled using browser storage (localStorage)
-Each user has their own separate task list
-Logout option is available

📝 Task Management---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-Add new tasks easily
-Mark tasks as completed or incomplete
-Delete tasks when no longer needed
-Tasks are saved automatically in the browser
-Data remains even after refreshing the page

🔍 Task Filtering-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Users can view tasks in three ways:

-All tasks
-Active tasks (not completed)
-Completed tasks

🔔 Daily Reminder System-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The app checks for pending tasks automatically
Between 9 PM and 12 AM, it reminds the user about incomplete tasks

A browser alert is shown to notify the user:

“You still have pending tasks to complete before the day ends!”

🎨 UI and Design---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-Clean and modern interface
-Fully responsive for mobile, tablet, and desktop
-Soft and aesthetic color theme
-Smooth transitions and hover effects
-Dark mode support (optional)

📱 Responsiveness----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The application is designed with a mobile-first approach and works smoothly 
on all screen sizes, including smartphones, tablets, and desktops.

🧱 Technologies Used---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

HTML5 – Structure of the app
CSS3 – Styling and responsive design (Flexbox/Grid)
JavaScript (ES6) – Application logic and functionality
localStorage – Data storage in the browser

*No frameworks or backend services are used.*

📁 Project Structure-------------------------------------------------------------------

index.html   → Intro page(SWIPE-UP)
home.html    → Main Page 
style.css    → Styling and layout
script.js    → Application logic

⚙️ How It Works-------------------------------------------------------------------------

A user signs up and their data is stored in the browser.
On login, the app loads that user’s saved tasks.
Tasks are added, updated, or deleted using JavaScript.
All changes are saved automatically in localStorage.
The app checks time and shows reminders for pending tasks in the evening.

🚀 How to Run the Project----------------------------------------------------------------

Download the project files
Open index.html in any browser
The app will run instantly.

*No installation or setup is required.*

🌐 Deployment-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

*This project can be easily deployed using:*

GitHub Pages
Netlify (drag and drop method)

📌 Summary--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TaskFlow is a lightweight productivity tool that demonstrates how a full-featured task management system 
can be built using only frontend technologies. It includes authentication, task tracking, filtering, and 
reminders in a clean and responsive design.
